      ### Summary
      2
      Voting Classifier is the best model out of the 3 models. The three models has the same f1-score which is 0.97, so we look to precision and recall values. Out of the three models, voting classifier achieved the best score between precision and recall. Voting classifier scores 0.95 which is the lowest of out the three models, however the recall score of 0.98 which scored highest among all 3 models, improves the quality of the model.
